author: Русское Общественное Движение «Возрождение. Золотой Век»
title: Просто новости из России и паразитического дикого Запада - 300 - Новости РуАН
text:
Британские учёные не смогли объяснить, как землетрясение на Камчатке вызвало цунами на западном берегу США.
Подсчитано: ещё пара таких землетрясений и о.Сахалин сдвинется настолько, что станет японским, но без японцев.
Сразу после заявления Трампа о двух американских подлодках Конгресс на всякий случай ушёл в краткосрочный отпуск до сентября.
Узнав о снятии Россией моратория на размещение РСМД, европарламентарии массово начали писать заявления на долгосрочный отпуск.
Мария Захарова заявила, что Россия не планирует размещение «Орешника» на Кубе и в Венесуэле. Кстати, именно так, с отрицания и открытия дискуссии, обычно начинает свою монотонную работу окно Овертона.
Трамп расценивает закупки странами российской нефти как финансирование боевых действия на Украине, а прямые поставки американского оружия ВСУ – как миролюбивое принуждение к мирному процессу. Смотрите, не перепутайте.
6 августа весь цивилизованный мир отмечает день спасения многих тысяч жизней с помощью гуманитарной ядерной бомбардировки Хиросимы и Нагасаки. Какие вам ещё нужны доказательства?
Генсек ООН Гутерриш прибыл в Хиросиму, чтобы поздравить жителей с чудесным спасением, но в поздравительной речи ни разу не упомянул имя спасителей.
6 августа прошлого года бандеровцы планировали учредить день спасения жителей Курской области, но традиционно самоликвидировались.
Спецпосланник Трампа Стив Уиткофф срочно прилетел в Москву для встречи с Дмитрием Медведевым. Для разогрева ему подсунули Кирилла Дмитриева, а прямо сейчас Владимира Путина.
Зеленский снялся на фоне Харькова.
Замечено: фондовые рынки перестаёт штормить, как только Трамп засыпает и начинает штормить, как только он открывает глаза.
Чрезвычайная эффективность внешней политики Трампа привела к тому, что в ответ на его угрозы Америку по какому-то адресу сразу отправили Бразилия, Россия, Индия, Китай и ЮАР. Не напомните первоначальный состав объединения БРИКС?
Трампу осталось два дня до следующей порции угроз.
Александр Дубровский

author: Press Trust of India
title: UK sanctions 1 million pounds for World Wars Memorial for Muslim soldiers - India Today
text: The UK government has sanctioned one million pounds towards a new World Wars Muslim Memorial to honour the sacrifice of Muslim soldiers who fought in the British Armed Forces in the two world wars including Indian Muslims recruited to the British Indian Army during the colonial eraAccording to the World Wars Muslim Memorial Trust WWMMT a registered charity created to campaign for such a memorial more than 750000 Muslims served in the Indian and Allied armies during both world wars of whom approximately 147000 were killed UK Chancellor Jeremy Hunt announced the funding for the new memorial in his Spring Budget speech in the House of Commons this weekldquoWhatever your faith colour or class this country will never forget the sacrifices made for our futurerdquo he told MPsThe memorial will be created in the National Memorial Arboretum at Staffordshire in the West Midlands region of EnglandThe arboretum is a 150-acre site on the edge of the National Forest which is dedicated to remembering those who served and sacrificed their lives for BritainThe new memorial will take its place alongside commemorative memorials on behalf of Sikhs Gurkhas and others providing an important place for reflection by communities who lost relatives as well as a place for those who wish to learn more about Britainrsquos rich and diverse history WWMMT saidldquoOur project coincides with the widespread re-evaluation of colonial history and the role Muslims play in a dynamic and changing modern Britainrdquo said Sir William Blackburne chair of the TrustquotWe want to emphasise shared sacrifices a common history and values and an inclusive programme of education for everyone in the UK ndash Muslims and non-Muslims alike The memorial will be a physical reminder of how people of all faiths make an impact working together and can continue to do so despite the challenges of those who attempt to divide our societyquot he saidThe memorial will take the shape of a minaret which is an integral part of mosque architecture all over the world A low exedra wall will be inscribed with stories of Muslim soldiers who fought in the name of the British crown Materials for construction will be hard-wearing brick and terracotta sourced from different parts of the UKSajid Javid a British Muslim Conservative member of Parliament who was credited for his campaign in its favour by Jeremy Hunt said quotThe service of British Muslim soldiers in the UK armed forces deserves recognition at the National Memorial ArboretumquotThanks to this announcement by the Chancellor and the excellent campaigning of the World Wars Muslim Memorial Trust this vision will now become a reality I am delighted to have supported the campaign which will have an enduring legacy for years to comequotonPublished By Ajmal Published On Mar 8 2024Tune InALSO READ UK PM Sunak denies his party has 039Islamophobic tendencies039 after Anderson039s commentsTrending Reel

title: Às vésperas da estreia na Série B com Paysandu, Robinho relembra passagem pelo Santos: "Cheguei lá um jovem e saí como um homem" | paysandu | ge
text:
O meia Robinho vive a expectativa de mais uma estreia com a camisa do Paysandu . O Papão encara o Santos , neste sábado, dia 20, pela 1ª rodada da Série B do Brasileiro. O camisa 20 bicolor conhece bem o adversário, jogou no Peixe logo no começo da carreira. Foram três temporadas no time paulista - 2008, 2009 e 2011 -, somando 58 jogos.
- É sempre especial voltar ao estádio da Vila Belmiro. Cheguei lá um jovem e sai como um homem. Depois, tive a oportunidade de enfrentá-los várias vezes. Já dei sete assistências para gols em jogos diante do Santos. Vai ser uma partida difícil. Fizeram um grande Paulista e, sem dúvida, entrarão como principal favorito ao acesso. Mas, o nosso time tem qualidade e uma equipe experiente, bem comandada pelo Hélio dos Anjos. Nos preparamos para fazermos uma grande estreia - disse o meia.
1 de 2 Robinho no Santos — Foto: Reprodução Robinho no Santos — Foto: Reprodução
Aos 36 anos, Robinho vem sendo titular nos últimos jogos do Paysandu e, contra o Peixe, provavelmente, não vai ser diferente. Nesta temporada, o meia já atuou em 14 jogos. Ele é um dos remanescentes do elenco que conquistou o acesso do Papão para a Série B, no ano passado. Ao todo, ele já jogou 38 partidas com a camisa bicolor.
2 de 2 Robinho, meia do Paysandu — Foto: Jorge Luís Totti/Paysandu Robinho, meia do Paysandu — Foto: Jorge Luís Totti/Paysandu

Santos e Paysandu se enfrentam neste sábado, às 16h30, na Vila Belmiro. A TV Liberal transmite a partida ao vivo e o ge Pará acompanha todos os lances do duelo em Tempo Real.

author: Tom Sileo
title: Service & Sacrifice: Keeping Us Safe
text:
Service & Sacrifice: Keeping Us Safe
A snapshot of the burdens being shouldered by brave U.S. troops and military families around the world.
Middle East
As
chaos continues in the Middle East, more than 1,500 U.S. military service members are headed to the troubled region to fight terrorism.
Earlier this week, a large ceremony was held at a sports arena in Trenton, New Jersey, to bid farewell to the state’s deploying National Guard soldiers. The brave men and women in uniform will be tasked with fighting ISIS in Syria and Iraq, where Iran-backed terrorist groups have
launched well over 100 attacks since Hamas terrorists attacked Israel in October.
“It is the largest deployment of New Jersey Army National Guard soldiers since 2008,” according to U.S. Central Command.
One of the departing soldiers is Lt. Col. Omar Minott, who
spoke to CBS Philadelphia about how his deployment will impact his loved ones.
“With a two-parent household, having me leave is a challenge with our four kids,” Lt. Col. Minott told the TV station. “But my wife is … she’s pretty strong.”
Please join The Stream in praying for the safety of these 1,500-plus soldiers and the well-being of their families here at home. America is grateful for your selfless service and willingness to confront the evils of terrorism.
Please Support The Stream: Equipping Christians to Think Clearly About the Political, Economic, and Moral Issues of Our Day. []()
Nothing could demonstrate the sacrifices of our military more than this week’s news that two U.S. Navy SEALs went missing off the coast of Somalia.
The SEALs, who went missing last Thursday, “were boarding an un-flagged vessel at night when one fell into the ocean. Another SEAL jumped in to rescue him,”
according to KPBS. Iranian missiles were later found by the SEAL team upon boarding the ship, which was bound for Yemen.
“That effort it is ongoing,” U.S. Air Force Gen. Pat Ryder said about the search for the missing SEALs during a Wednesday news conference at the Pentagon. “Certainly, you know, we hope that we are able to recover our teammates. Our thoughts and prayers are clearly with their families at this time.”
As we pray for the safety of the missing SEALs, the U.S. military is pounding terrorist targets in Yemen, where the Iranian-backed Houthis have been launching attacks on U.S. Navy and commercial ships in the Red Sea. According to the military, American ships and submarines took out 14 Iranian missiles during Wednesday’s wave of counterattacks.
“The actions by the Iranian-backed Houthi terrorists continue to endanger international mariners and disrupt the commercial shipping lanes in the southern Red Sea and adjacent waterways,” said Gen. Michael Erik Kurilla in a statement
posted on X. “We will continue to take actions to protect the lives of innocent mariners and we will always protect our people.”
Please continue to pray for our nation’s valiant troops and their families.
Coming Home
A squadron of U.S. Navy pilots returned to their Virginia Beach base earlier this week after spending eight long months patrolling the Mediterranean Sea.
Welcome home, heroes! Thanks to you and your families for sacrificing so much to keep our country safe.
Tom Sileo is a contributing senior editor of The Stream. He is the author of the forthcoming I Have Your Back, the recently released Be Bold and co-author of Three Wise Men, Brothers Forever, 8 Seconds of Courage and Fire in My Eyes. Follow Tom on X @TSileo and The Stream at @Streamdotorg.
